---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const sectionHeading = "font-display text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Notice — Voia"
  description="How Voia collects, uses, and protects the details you share through our enquiry form and chat assistant."
>
  <main class="flex-1">
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 pt-8 sm:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink md:text-4xl">Privacy Notice</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 max-w-prose text-lg text-sand-700">
        A plain-language explanation of what we collect through our enquiry form and chat
        assistant, why, and how to ask us to change or delete it.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl space-y-8 px-6 py-8 sm:px-8">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-amber-50 p-4 text-sm text-amber-800">
        <strong>TODO:</strong> real contact email + retention period need to be filled in before
        this site goes live — see the placeholders below.
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class={sectionHeading}>What we collect</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink">
          When you submit our enquiry form, we collect your name, your email address, and any
          trip details or message you choose to share — for example the trip or destination
          you're asking about, travel dates, traveller numbers, or a note to us.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class={sectionHeading}>Why we collect it</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink">
          Only to reply to your enquiry and help you plan your trip. We don't use it for anything
          else.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class={sectionHeading}>Our lawful basis</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink">
          Your consent — given when you tick the consent checkbox on the enquiry form before
          submitting it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class={sectionHeading}>Who can see it</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink">
          Only Voia's admin, via our secure backend. The website itself can only submit new
          enquiries — it has no way to read them back. We don't sell your data, and we don't run
          advertising trackers on this form.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class={sectionHeading}>How long we keep it</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink">
          <em>TODO: retention period to be confirmed.</em> We'll keep your enquiry only for as
          long as we need it to reply to you and follow up, and no longer than that.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class={sectionHeading}>The chat assistant</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink">
          When you chat with Voia, your messages are sent to Google's Gemini API to generate a reply.
          We also save an anonymous copy of the conversation so we can learn what people ask and improve
          Voia. It's stored against a random session code only — <strong>no name, email, IP address, or
          device details are kept with it</strong>, and it isn't linked to you.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink">
          Please don't type personal details into the chat — for booking or anything personal, use our{" "}
          <a href="/contact" class="font-medium text-teal-700 underline hover:text-teal-800 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-teal-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2">enquiry form</a>{" "}
          instead. We keep these anonymous transcripts for up to about a month and then delete them; our
          lawful basis is our legitimate interest in improving the service. As with enquiries, the website
          itself can only add new transcripts — it can never read them back.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class={sectionHeading}>Your rights</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink">
          You can ask us what we hold about you, or ask us to correct or delete it, at any time —
          just email us (see below).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class={sectionHeading}>Contact us</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink">
          <em>TODO: replace with a real contact address.</em> For now, reach us at{" "}
          <a
            href="mailto:hello@voia.example"
            class="font-medium text-teal-700 underline hover:text-teal-800 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-teal-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
          >
            hello@voia.example
          </a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-sand-200 px-6 py-8 text-center sm:px-8">
    <p class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-coral-700">Voia</p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-sand-700">Travel the way you feel.</p>
    <nav aria-label="Footer" class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1">
      <a href="/about" class="inline-flex min-h-11 items-center rounded-md px-2 text-sm font-medium text-sand-700 transition-colors hover:text-coral-700 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-coral-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2">
        About
      </a>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex min-h-11 items-center rounded-md px-2 text-sm font-medium text-sand-700 transition-colors hover:text-coral-700 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-coral-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2">
        Contact
      </a>
    </nav>
    <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-sand-600">A university project.</p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
